Plot:

Work It Outâ€¦ The Malibu Way! When Ashlyn Gere and her cute co-workers at a seaside health club end up owning the place, they think they have a goldmine on their hands. But when the big bucks fail to come in, the girls use their more physical assets to draw customers. The plan works - and the girls end up with a slew of studly members who may not build up their pecs but sure work out their love muscles!



Good sex and high production values complement each other in this internationally-cast scorcher from Alex DeRenzy. Jon Dough donates his Malibu Fitness Center to its employees for tax reasons. Sure! Don't be fooled by that dream orgy early on. What Jeanna Fine and K.C. Williams do with Sean Michaels and T.T. Boy most definitely will turn the viewer on. There's far too much sex to mention it all, but excellent horizontal (and sometimes vertical) performances are supplied by Angela Summers (twice!), Jeanna Fine (ditto), K.C. Williams (ditto yet again), and Ashlyn Gere's session with Joey Silvera is almost as hot as their coupling in last year's Bush Pilots. When the sex is good, it's great!
